stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Proposed: 親 Agent が DelegateIntent を提案する
  Proposed --> Validated: 结构与范围通过
  Validated --> Rejected: 越界/缺少能力
  Validated --> Running: permission allow
  Running --> NeedsApproval: 子 Agent 请求高风险动作
  NeedsApproval --> Running: 親 Agent/ユーザーが承認
  NeedsApproval --> Constrained: 拒绝并收窄范围
  Constrained --> Running: 继续只做安全子集
  Running --> Completed: 構造化結果を返す
  Running --> Failed: timeout/cancel/tool failure
  Failed --> Recovered: 親 Agent が回収または再委任
  Completed --> Joined: 親 Agent review & join
  Recovered --> Joined
  Rejected --> Joined
  Joined --> [*]
